Configuration
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Make sure you have vhost.tcl added in sbnc.tcl,
and edit the settings in inc/settings.php

Example configuration:

//sBNC Server Settings
$ip = 'localhost';      //sBNC IP
$port = '9000';		//sBNC Port
$webroot = '/sbnc';     //Where the Interface is located

//Interface Settings

$default_lang = "en";
//Available languages:
English - en
Swedish - sv
German - de
Finnish - fi
Urdu - pk


$default_style = "grey";
//Available styles:
grey
black.

//Name of the interface.
$name = "ShroundBNC Webinterface";

//How long cookies should last, default 30days.
$expire = time()+60*60*24*30;
